      "text": "You know, because many people this time, already raped, and already-- if not raped, just-- just want to get a piece more bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because was a doctor, already, who examined you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they saw how I cannot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So a Jeep took us and my sister-- I don't want to go with her-- to a hospital, which is, actually, wasn't a big hospital-- for the German who came back from the front, you know, from the war.",
