      "text": "And I get, every day, injection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and was a Russian doctor, and she saw what-- you know, I get the yellow, long robe, and too big.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I cut it with a knife.",
